T16TD4434E:210b-35: zhun mar dang sbyar la bsregs te snar bdug par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:210b-36: yang na sa he de ba dang /
T16TD4434E:210b-39: na khu li rnams btags te lhan cig tu sbyar ba bsregs te snar bdug go //
T16TD4434E:210b-40: yang rims zhi bar bya ba'i phyir sman de dag gong ma gnyis kyis lus bsku ba'am lus dril bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:210b-45: aa rdzun rnams kyi lo ma dang /
T16TD4434E:211a-0: 'di rnams btags la lhan cig tu sbyar te bsregs pas bdugs na yang @211a * //
T16TD4434E:211a-11: 'di rnams lhan cig tu sbyar ba'i bdug pa 'di'i ming ni gzhan gyis mi thub pa zhes bya ste /
T16TD4434E:211a-12: des bdugs na yang rims nad thams cad sel to //
T16TD4434E:211a-13: rgya skyegs kyi khu ba dang /
T16TD4434E:211a-14: til mar gnyis las srang sum cu rtsa gnyis gnyis dang /
T16TD4434E:211a-15: zho kha chu til mar gyi bzhi 'gyur gyi nang du /
T16TD4434E:211a-27: la phug rnams kyi phye ma lhan cig tu bskol te /
T16TD4434E:211a-28: til mar 'ba' zhig lus pa'i ming ni rgya skyegs la sogs pa'i mar zhes bya ste /
T16TD4434E:211a-29: des lus bsku ba la sogs pa byas na rims so cog dang /
T16TD4434E:211a-38: sgrum ma rnams la yang dge ba yin no //
T16TD4434E:211a-39: mi mkhris pa'i nang drag pos btab nas lus shin tu tsha bar gyur pa la ni /
T16TD4434E:211a-40: khong pa bsil zhing bser bu 'ong ba'i gnas su bzhag la /
T16TD4434E:211a-41: bsil ba'i cho ga 'og nas 'byung ba 'di dag bya'o //
T16TD4434E:211a-42: de la bsil bar bya ba'i cho ga ni skyu ru ra mar gyi nang du brngos te btab pa'i phye ma rtsabs skyur pos 'dag gu byas pas lus la bskus na tsha ba zhi bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:211a-44: rgya shug gi lo ma brdungs te /
T16TD4434E:211a-46: nya lcibs shin tu bsil ba 'am /
T16TD4434E:211a-47: rtsva d'urba btags pa rtsabs skyur bas btab pa 'am /
T16TD4434E:211a-48: 'dam shin tu bsil bas lus thams cad bsku bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:211a-49: yang na sngar smos pa'i shing n+ya gro dha la sogs sman gyi sde tshan nam /
T16TD4434E:211b-0: me tog autpal la sogs pa sman gyi sde tshan @211b phye mar byas la /
T16TD4434E:211b-1: rtsabs skyur po dang sbyar bas lus la bsku bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:211b-2: yang na sman gyi sde tshan de gnyis las gang yang rung ba skol ba'i khu ba bsgrangs ba'i nang du /
T16TD4434E:211b-3: tsha ba mi bzod pa'i mi nyid 'ju bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:211b-4: yang na bu ram chang ngam /
T16TD4434E:211b-8: 'o ma'i rgun lus la byug na yang tsha ba sel te bzang ngo //
T16TD4434E:211b-25: skyu ru ra dang nye'u shing rnams lhan cig tu skol ba'i khu ba'i nang du /
T16TD4434E:211b-26: sman de dag nyid kyi phye ma dang /
T16TD4434E:211b-27: rgya skyegs kyi khu ba dang /
T16TD4434E:211b-31: zho kha chu dang til mar rnams blugs te bskol la til mar nyi tshe lus par byas la btsags pa 'di ni pags pa'i mdog bzang zhing /
T16TD4434E:211b-33: skom pa'i nad sel pa'i mchog yin te lus la bsku bar bya'o ;
T16TD4434E:211b-38: btsag rnams btags la zhun mar dang sbyar te mgor bskus na yang skom pa'i nad dang /
T16TD4434E:211b-39: lus tsha ba'i gnod pa sel to //
T16TD4434E:211b-44: kha lung rnams btags la zhun mar dang sbyar /
T16TD4434E:211b-45: 'dis kyang skom pa'i nad dang lus tsha ba sel to //
T16TD4434E:211b-48: chu shing gi lo ma dang nyi snga [?] ba'i steng du nyal la /
T16TD4434E:211b-49: shing t'a la'i lo ma tsan dan brdar ba'i khu ba'i nang du dmyugs pa'i bsil g-yob kyis g-yabs na yang lus tsha ba'i gnod pa sel to //
T16TD4434E:211b-50: rdzing bu'i me tog padma kha bye ba dang ldan pa'i phyogs sam /
T16TD4434E:211b-51: chu 'dren ba'i 'khrul 'khor yong ba'i phyogs su bsil khang bzang po byas pa'i nang du 'dug cing /
T16TD4434E:212a-0: bud med kyi lus tsan dan gyi 'dag @212a * //
T16TD4434E:212a-1: gus byugs pas mthar sbyar na yang /
T16TD4434E:212a-2: lus tsha ba'i gnod pa sel to /
T16TD4434E:212a-5: rlung gi rims kyis thebs te /
T16TD4434E:212a-6: grang bas nyen pa'i cho ga bshad de /
T16TD4434E:212a-7: de ltar grang bas nyen pa la ni /
T16TD4434E:212a-8: khyim dron po'i nang du 'dug la rdul gdon pa'i dugs bya zhing gos lci ba la sogs pa bgo bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:212a-16: shu dag rnams lhan cig sbyar bas lus byug cing de dag bsregs pas lus bdugs na yang grang ba sel to //
T16TD4434E:212a-17: yang na sman de dag nyid btags pa'i phye ma dang /
T16TD4434E:212a-19: nas tshig 'khus pa'i thal ba dang /
T16TD4434E:212a-20: tshva dang rtsabs skyur ba la sogs pa dang /
T16TD4434E:212a-21: til mar rnams lhan cig tu skol ba'i til mar nyi tshe lus pas lus la bskus na yang grang ba sel to //
T16TD4434E:212a-24: tshva dron pos lus la byug gam /
T16TD4434E:212a-25: yang na byi'u rug pa dang /
T16TD4434E:212a-27: shi kru rnams brdungs pas lus la bskus na yang grang ba sel to //
T16TD4434E:212a-28: yang na sbrebs par gyur pa la ni rlung sel ba'i rtsi shing rnams dang /
T16TD4434E:212a-29: gso ma brdungs ba'i khu ba dron po'i nang du /
T16TD4434E:212a-31: yang na thang shing dang aa ka ru bsregs pas bdug gam /
T16TD4434E:212a-33: ksha bu ka bsregs pas bdug par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:212a-34: bud med lang tsho la bab pa nu ma rgyas shing 'bur la yid tsam dbyibs dgu zhing /
T16TD4434E:212a-35: rked pa la sogs pa'i lus /
T16TD4434E:212a-36: aa ka ru'i lde gus byugs pa dang /
T16TD4434E:212a-37: mthar sbyar na yang grang ba shin tu sbrebs pa med par byed do /
T16TD4434E:212a-39: // / da ni rims nad can gyi kha zas kyi bye brag bshad de /
T16TD4434E:212a-41: kha zas 'bras s'a lu shun lpags dmar po la sogs pa dang /
T16TD4434E:212a-42: 'bras zhag drug cus smin pa bzang ngo //
T16TD4434E:212b-1: mon sran na gu bzang ngo //
T16TD4434E:212b-9: gong ma sreg rnams kyi sha bzang ngo //
T16TD4434E:212b-10: tshod ma ni shing pa ta la'i lo ma dang /
T16TD4434E:212b-12: karko ta la sogs pa bzang ngo //
T16TD4434E:212b-13: de la cho gar bsrung ba'i mdo ni /
T16TD4434E:212b-15: rims byang nas nyams ma brtas kyi bar du kha zas lci ba dang /
T16TD4434E:212b-19: mgo mi 'thub ste ngal bar gyur pa rnams bsgrims te bsdad par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:212b-20: rims la nad bla gnyan 'byung ba mgo 'khor ba dang /
T16TD4434E:212b-23: skyug pa la sogs par gyur na /
T16TD4434E:212b-24: rims nyid la gnod par mi 'gyur ba'i so so'i sman gang 'os pa rnams kyis de bsal bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:212b-25: rims drag po 'byung du mi btub cing cho ga gzhan gyis ma slon pa la ni sman chen po lus la gdags pa dang /
T16TD4434E:212b-26: sman gyi khu ba'am sngags chus khrus bya ba dang /
T16TD4434E:212b-31: grub pa'i sngags kyi cho ga rgyas par bya ba rnams kyis zhi bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:212b-32: rims nad byung ba'i mtshan ma ni /
T16TD4434E:212b-38: khar 'byung ba rnams la rtogs par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:212b-39: rims nad gso ba'i le'u ste lnga pa rdzogs so /
T16TD4434E:212b-42: nad pa zad par ma shes te /
T16TD4434E:212b-43: gya tshom du sman gyi las byas na /
T16TD4434E:212b-44: ngal gyi snon de las sto bar zad do //
T16TD4434E:212b-45: de bas na phrin pa dang /
T16TD4434E:212b-47: mtshan ma 'di gsum las tshe rtogs par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:212b-48: de 'chi ltas ni 'chi bar 'gyur ba de'i ngang tshul dang /
T16TD4434E:212b-51: spyod pa'i tshul rnams 'gyur ba gang yin pa de dag ni /
T16TD4434E:212b-52: mdor na sman pa mchog gis 'chi ltas su rig par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:213a-0: de la dbang po rnams don @213a * //
T16TD4434E:213a-2: sman pa dang mdza' bo bla ma la sdang zhing dgra la dga' bar gyur pa gang yin pa de ni 'chi bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:213a-3: nam thang ba la sprin dang /
T16TD4434E:213a-6: gzhal med khang dang bzhon pa rnams kyis nam mkha' khebs par mthong ba gang yin pa de ni 'tsho bar mi 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:213a-7: skar ma lha mo sgrib med ces bya ba dang /
T16TD4434E:213a-9: dgu tshigs mi mthong ba dang /
T16TD4434E:213a-10: sa chen po gom pa brgyad khor khor yug tsam du chung ngur mthong ba de ni srog gi dbang po 'das zin pa yin no //
T16TD4434E:213a-11: nyin par skar ma me 'bar ba 'dra ba mthong ba dang /
T16TD4434E:213a-12: nyi ma'i mdog kha dog sna tshogs su mthong ba dang /
T16TD4434E:213a-13: rlung la gzugs yod par mthong ba gang yin pa de ni nges par 'chi bar bstan to //
T16TD4434E:213a-14: nyi ma 'char ba'i ngos la bu gu dod par mthong ba dang /
T16TD4434E:213a-15: mar me shi ba'i dri snar mi tshor ba de ni 'chi bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:213a-16: me long la sogs pa la bdag gi gzugs brnyan yan lag ma tshang bar mthong ngam /
T16TD4434E:213a-17: yang na ye med par mthong ba dang /
T16TD4434E:213a-18: sems can sna tshogs kyi cha byad mthong na de ni gshin rje'i khyim na gnas pa yin no //
T16TD4434E:213a-19: mig g-yon pa khung du bros pa 'am /
T16TD4434E:213a-22: mchu nag por gyur cing dbyibs nyams sam /
T16TD4434E:213a-23: kha mnam por gyur pa gang yin pa de ni spang bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:213a-24: mig dmar por gyur pa dang /
T16TD4434E:213a-25: mig dmar bar gyur pa dang /
T16TD4434E:213a-30: ya yor gyur pa de ni ror gyur par shes par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:213a-31: bzhin gyi mdog dmar pa dang /
T16TD4434E:213a-34: sdo sangs su gyur pa dang /
T16TD4434E:213a-36: mdog mi sdug par gyur pa dang /
T16TD4434E:213a-37: dran pa nyams pa gang yin pa de'i tshe ni 'das zin par shes par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:213b-0: mgo bo la ba lang gi lci ba'i phye mas stug por khebs pa @213b lta bur snang ba dang /
T16TD4434E:213b-3: so mdog mi sdug par gyur cing zho byung bar gyur na /
T16TD4434E:213b-4: de ni tshe zad par shes par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:213b-10: dkar po lta bur gyur pa gang la snang ba ni gshin rje'i khyim du 'gro bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:213b-11: dpral ba la shig 'gro ba dang /
T16TD4434E:213b-12: gtor ma bya rog mi 'dod pa dang /
T16TD4434E:213b-13: ha cang gnyid che ba dang /
T16TD4434E:213b-14: ha cang gnyid med par gyur pa de'i tshe ni ring por mi thub po /
T16TD4434E:213b-21: mur 'gram gyi sha lhod pa dang /
T16TD4434E:213b-22: sha 'phyang bar gyur ba gang yin pa de ni srog ring por mi thogs par spong bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:213b-23: sha bros la skad kyi gdang sa che bar gyur pa dang /
T16TD4434E:213b-24: nyams stobs yod bzhin du skad zhom par gyur pa dang /
T16TD4434E:213b-25: skra mtshams bye ba gang yin pa de 'chi ba'i dus kyi zhags pas zin par shes par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:213b-26: kha zas zos kyang sha bros pa dang /
T16TD4434E:213b-27: kha zas ma zos kyang nyams stobs skye ba dang /
T16TD4434E:213b-28: bzhin gyi mdog snum par gyur tam /
T16TD4434E:213b-29: kha dog gzhan du gyur pa de ni srog gi dbang po 'das zin pa yin no //
T16TD4434E:213b-30: glo bur du dri mi zhim pa dang /
T16TD4434E:213b-31: dri mi zhim pa zhig tu gyur tam /
T16TD4434E:213b-32: sbrang ma sngon po 'khor bar gyur na de 'chi bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:213b-33: da ni mtshan ma'i bye brag bshad de /
T16TD4434E:213b-34: rmi lam du lus snum gyis byugs pa dang /
T16TD4434E:213b-40: rnga mo la zhon pa rmi lam mi bzang ngo //
T16TD4434E:213b-41: bud med skra bshig cing gos nag po dang /
T16TD4434E:213b-42: dmar bag gyon pas bcings te dgod bzhin du lho phyogs su khrid pa rmis na mi 'dod pa yin no //
T16TD4434E:213b-44: mu stegs can gyi rab tu byung ba la sogs pa dang phrad pa dang /
T16TD4434E:214a-0: 'ji bas lus byugs te gar byed pa @214a * //
T16TD4434E:214a-3: brag la sogs pa las lhung ba dang /
T16TD4434E:214a-6: bya rog la sogs pas mchus btsugs pa dang /
T16TD4434E:214a-7: lhung ba rmis na mi dge'o //
T16TD4434E:214a-11: shing pa ri pattra rnams la 'dzegs pa dang /
T16TD4434E:214a-14: 'bru mar btsir ba'i tshigs ma dang /
T16TD4434E:214a-15: lcags rnyed pa rmis na mi rung bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:214a-16: rmi lam na bag ma len pa dang /
T16TD4434E:214a-17: me tog dmar po'i phreng ba thogs shing gos dmar bag gyon pa dang /
T16TD4434E:214a-19: sha btsos pa za zhing rmi ba ni mi 'dod pa yin no //
T16TD4434E:214a-20: rmi lam du rnam pa 'di lta bu dang /
T16TD4434E:214a-21: gzhan yang rnam pa sna tshogs de 'dra bdag mthong na /
T16TD4434E:214a-22: mi na pa ni nad kyis 'debs par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:214a-25: // / da ni mtshan ma bzang po'i bye brag bshad de /
T16TD4434E:214a-38: mi dge zhing des pa dang /
T16TD4434E:214a-39: bud med rgyan gyis brgyan pa mthong zhing rmis na bzang ngo //
T16TD4434E:214a-40: rmi lam du khyu ba dang /
T16TD4434E:214a-44: 'bras bu yod pa la 'chag pa dang /
T16TD4434E:214a-47: me tog gi phreng ba rnyed pa dang /
T16TD4434E:214a-48: chu chen po las brgal ba rmis na /
T16TD4434E:214a-49: mi na bas ni nor rnyed par 'gyur /
T16TD4434E:214a-50: nad pa zhig na ni nad myur du 'tsho bar 'gyur ro /
T16TD4434E:214a-52: // / da ni phrin pa'i phye brag bshad de /
T16TD4434E:214a-55: mu stegs can gyi rab tu byung ba la sogs pa'am /
T16TD4434E:214a-57: dbyig pa lag na thogs shing /
T16TD4434E:214a-58: rgod bag tu gyur pa dang /
T16TD4434E:214b-2: 'di rnams mi 'dod pa yin par bshad do //
T16TD4434E:214b-3: phrin pa lag pa nyed pa dang /
T16TD4434E:214b-5: mgo lus mar gyis byugs pa dang /
T16TD4434E:214b-8: ma ning phrin par 'od ba dang /
T16TD4434E:214b-9: bud med kyi rtsig gi ming dang /
T16TD4434E:214b-10: ldan pa sna la sogs pa dang /
T16TD4434E:214b-11: ma ning gi rtsig gi ming dang ldan ba /
T16TD4434E:214b-12: mig la sogs pa la lag gis nom pa dang /
T16TD4434E:214b-13: pho mtshan gyi phyogs su lag pas nom pa dang /
T16TD4434E:214b-16: ma he zhon te 'ongs pa dang /
T16TD4434E:214b-17: bsdad cing du:khar smra ba 'di dag ni mi rung ba yin no //
T16TD4434E:214b-18: de dag las ldog pa ni dge ba yin no //
T16TD4434E:214b-19: sman pa nad pa'i gan du 'gro bar chas pa na /
T16TD4434E:214b-20: glang po che'i skad thos pa dang /
T16TD4434E:214b-22: rnga sgra la sogs pa thos pa dang /
T16TD4434E:214b-24: me tog gi phreng ba dang /
T16TD4434E:214b-27: bum pa gang ba la sogs pa mthong na bzang ngo //
T16TD4434E:214b-28: sman pa chas te 'gro ba na /
T16TD4434E:214b-31: phug ron la sogs pa g-yon logs na gnas shing snang la /
T16TD4434E:214b-32: mo'i ming dang ldan pa skyung ka dang /
T16TD4434E:214b-33: ri skegs la sogs pa g-yas logs na gnas shing snang ste /
T16TD4434E:214b-34: nad pa'i khyim gyi nang du 'gro ba'i tshe legs par bsu na bya ba de don du 'gyur bar shes par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:214b-38: 'bras bu dang me tog yod pa'i shing mthong ba dang //
T16TD4434E:214b-39: g-yas logs sam g-yon logs nas bya 'phur ram 'dug cing skad snyan pa sgrog pa thams cad kyang dge ba yin no //
T16TD4434E:214b-40: khyi dang wa g-yas phyogs su song na dge'o //
T16TD4434E:214b-43: klu sbrul mthong ba ni dus thams cad du mi 'dod pa yin no //
T16TD4434E:214b-44: de ltar sman pa gang gis bsgrims te legs par brtags shing bye brag phyed par byas nas las nges par rtsom pa de'i grags pa ni dge ba mang po tshogs pa'i nang du me tog gi phreng ba rnying pa bzhin du mdzes par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:215a-0: @215a * // 'chi ltas kyi le'u ste drug pa rdzogs so /
T16TD4434E:215a-2: // / da ni 'khru ba gso ba'i le'u bshad par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:215a-3: de la 'khru ba ni kha zas mi 'phrod pa dang /

T16TD4434E:215a-8: ha cang mang du za ba dang /
T16TD4434E:215a-9: ha cang nyung du za ba la sogs pas me drod med par byas nas /
T16TD4434E:215a-10: nad gzhi shas rnyed pa las 'khru bar 'gyur te /

T16TD4434E:215a-12: kun 'dus pa las gyur pa dang /
T16TD4434E:215a-13: mya ngan las gyur pa dang /
T16TD4434E:215a-14: 'jigs pa las gyur pa dang rnam pa drug yod de /

T16TD4434E:215a-16: de la rlung las gyur pa'i 'khru ba'i mtshan ma ni /
T16TD4434E:215a-17: phyi sa 'i mdog rtsa dmar ba dang /

T16TD4434E:215a-19: nyung du nyung bar 'gyur ba dang /
T16TD4434E:215a-20: yang dang yang du 'byung ba dang /
T16TD4434E:215a-23: sgra dang bcas su 'byung ba rnams so //
T16TD4434E:215a-24: mkhris pa las gyur pa'i 'khru ba'i mtshan ma ni /
T16TD4434E:215a-25: phyi sa'i mdog ser ba dang /
T16TD4434E:215a-32: gzhang kha tsha 'ur 'ur por gyur cing 'brum ba 'byung ba dang /
T16TD4434E:215a-33: skom dad che bar gyur pa rnams yin no //
T16TD4434E:215a-34: bad kan las gyur pa'i 'khru ba'i mtshan ma ni /
T16TD4434E:215a-35: phyi sa'i mdog dkar ba dang ;
T16TD4434E:215a-42: brang tsha zhing kha nas chu 'byung ba rnams yin no //
T16TD4434E:215a-43: nad gzhi gsum char 'dus pa las gyur pa'i 'khru ba'i mtshan ma ni /
T16TD4434E:215a-44: phyi sa phag tshil 'dra ba dang /
T16TD4434E:215a-47: sha bkrus pa'i khu ba 'dra ba rnams yin te gso dka' bar shes par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:215a-48: phyi sa sbrang rtsi 'dra ba dang /
T16TD4434E:215a-50: mchin pa'i dum bu 'dra ba 'byung ba dang /
T16TD4434E:215b-1: sha brdungs brdungs pa 'dra ba dang /
T16TD4434E:215b-2: tshon sna tshogs su 'dug pa dang /
T16TD4434E:215b-3: dri shin tu dku ba dang /
T16TD4434E:215b-4: zhag tshig tshig po yod pa ni mi 'tsho /
T16TD4434E:215b-8: dbugs mi bde ba la sogs pa'i nang bla gnyan gyis thebs pa dang /

T16TD4434E:230a-22: bad kan las gyur pa'i dmu rdzings la ni thog mar 'jam rtsi pi pi ling la sogs pa dang sbyar ba'i sman mar sngar bshad pa btang nas dugs byas pa'i 'og tu /

T16TD4434E:270b-5: nag tshur rnams gyi phye ma ba ru ra'i mar dang chu'i nang du bskol te /
T16TD4434E:270b-6: ba ru ra'i mar nyi tshe lus pa btsags la zla ba gcig gi bar du lcags kyi snod du bzhag ste /
T16TD4434E:270b-7: mgo la bsku zhing snar blugs na /
T16TD4434E:270b-8: de ma thag tu dus la ma bab par skra dkar ba dang /
T16TD4434E:270b-9: dus la ba ba ste skra dkar ba med par byed do //
T16TD4434E:270b-14: zho kha chu rnams gang yang rung ba'i nang du bskol bas nub mo mgo la byugs la /
T16TD4434E:270b-15: nang par 'bras bu gsum bskol ba'i khu bas bkrus na skra nag por 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:270b-16: skra 'khor ling du byi ba la ni /
T16TD4434E:270b-17: sman sra ha ta'i khu ba sbrang rtsi dang sbyar te bskus na skye bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:270b-18: yang na 'ol ma se'i rtsa ba dang /
T16TD4434E:270b-19: 'bras bu gang yang rung ba ba gcin dang sbyar ba'am /
T16TD4434E:270b-20: yang na go bye'i khu bas byug par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:270b-21: shing pa ta'i myu gu dang /
T16TD4434E:270b-22: bhringga r'a dza'i phye ma sle tres kyi khu ba dang sbyar te nyi tshan gyi drod kyis bsros pas bskus na yang skra mi skye ba skye bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:270b-23: mig nad la phan par 'dod pas ni rtag tu mar btung ba dang /
T16TD4434E:270b-24: 'bras bu gsum gyi sman sbyar ba dang /
T16TD4434E:270b-26: bkru sman btang zhing kha zas su 'bras dang /
T16TD4434E:270b-29: ri dags skam san gnas pa'i sha bza' bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:270b-30: mig sman gyi rgyud kyi le'u rtsa drug pa rdzogs so /
T16TD4434E:270b-32: // / sman dpyad gces pa grub pa zhes bya ba /
T16TD4434E:270b-33: bam po bdun pa ste tha ma'o /
T16TD4434E:270b-35: // / de nas dug gso ba'i rgyud kyi le'u bshad par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:270b-37: sdig sbrul gyi za dug dang rnam pa gnyis so //
T16TD4434E:270b-38: de la rtsi dug ni rtsa ba la sogs pa'i rang bzhin /
T16TD4434E:270b-39: phyi ma ni sbrul la sogs pa las byung ba yin no //
T16TD4434E:270b-40: dug la phan gnod rnam pa bcu yod de /
T16TD4434E:270b-43: cha phras te rtsar 'gro ba dang /
T16TD4434E:271a-5: bad kan sdud cing 'dren pa dang /
T16TD4434E:271a-7: rno ba rnams yin par bshad do //
T16TD4434E:271a-8: sbrul ni mgo che ba'i rigs dang /
T16TD4434E:271a-10: khra bo'i rigs 'di gsum gyi bye brag las /
T16TD4434E:271a-11: rlung gi rang bzhin can dang /
T16TD4434E:271a-12: mkhris pa'i rang bzhin can dang /
T16TD4434E:271a-13: bad kan gyi rang bzhin can dang gsum yod par bshad de /
T16TD4434E:271a-14: go rim bzhin du so sor sbyar ro //
T16TD4434E:271a-15: rigs 'dres pa ni mtshan ma gnyis gnyis 'dres pa dang ldan pa yin no //
T16TD4434E:271a-16: de la sbrul mgo chen po'i rigs kyis zin pa ni /
T16TD4434E:271a-17: rma kha gnag pa yin no //
T16TD4434E:271a-18: rlung nad kyi rnam grangs dang /
T16TD4434E:271a-19: mtshan ma thams cad bskyed do //
T16TD4434E:271a-20: sbrul lus 'khyil ba'i rigs kyis zin pa ni /
T16TD4434E:271a-21: rma kha che la mdog ser zhing skrangs pa yin te /
T16TD4434E:271a-22: mkhris pa'i nad gyi sna grangs dang mtshan ma thams cad skyed do //
T16TD4434E:271a-23: sbrul khra bo'i rigs kyis zin pa ni /
T16TD4434E:271a-25: skrangs pa myur du 'dzub tu mi btub la 'byil zhing snum pa dang /
T16TD4434E:271a-26: khrag 'dzag pa shin tu bska ba rnams yin te /
T16TD4434E:271a-27: bad kan gyi nad kyi sna grangs dang /
T16TD4434E:271a-28: mchan ma thams cad skyed do //
T16TD4434E:271a-36: khrums smad rnams kyi nyin par sbrul gyis zin pa ni shin tu bsgrims na 'ga' zhig 'chi bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:271a-45: 'di rnams kyi dus su sbrul gyis zin pa yang mi bzad pa yin par bshad do //
T16TD4434E:271a-50: shin tu grang mos kyang ba spu mi ldang zhing /
T16TD4434E:271a-51: grang 'brum mi 'byung ba gang yin pa de ni sbang bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:271b-0: de la thog ma zin ma thag tu snying la dug mi 'dzin par bsrung @271b ba'i phyir smyur te mar sbyin no //
T16TD4434E:271b-1: de nas gang zin pa bcing ba dang /
T16TD4434E:271b-2: brdabs ru la sogs pas gzhib cing drang ba dang /
T16TD4434E:271b-3: gar zin pa chu bkor [?] du bcas pa dang /
T16TD4434E:271b-6: nyen kor nas gtar zhing khrag dbyung ba rnams bya bar bshad do //
T16TD4434E:271b-7: de la sbrul mgo chen po'i rigs kyis zin pa la ni /
T16TD4434E:271b-9: shve ti'i khu ba 'thungs na sel bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:271b-10: yang na srin bu bar dza'i rtsa ba'i phye ma rang gi khu ba dang brdzis te skams la slar yang brdzi zhing bskam pa de lta bur lan mang du bskol te btung bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:271b-11: sbrul lus 'khyil ba'i rigs kyis zin pa la ni /
T16TD4434E:271b-12: shing ba ta'i yal ga'i thor to dang /
T16TD4434E:271b-18: shing mngar rnams kyi phye ma 'bras bkrus pa'i khu ba'am chu bskol te bsgrangs ba dang sbyar ba btung ngo //
T16TD4434E:271b-19: sbrul khro bo'i rigs kyis zin pa la ni /
T16TD4434E:271b-27: khyim gyi dud pa rnams kyi phye mchu bskol ba grang mo dang sbyar te bzungs na dug sel bar byed do //
T16TD4434E:271b-35: ba lang gi mkhris pa rnams kyi phye ma chu dang sbyar te btsags la mig bskus na dug gis phog ste brgyal ba slar langs par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:271b-36: yang na na kta ma la dang /
T16TD4434E:271b-42: byi'u rug gi me tog dang /
T16TD4434E:271b-43: 'di rnams phye ma ra gcin dang sbyar te btsags pas mig bskus na yang slar dran par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:271b-44: ma yu ra ka'i sa bon dang /
T16TD4434E:271b-45: shi ri sha'i sa bon dang /
T16TD4434E:271b-46: rgyam tsha rnams kyi phye ma 'am /
T16TD4434E:271b-48: po son cha'i sa bon dang /
T16TD4434E:271b-49: pa ta rnams kyi phye ma chu dang sbyar te btsags pa snar blugs na yang slar dran bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:272a-1: rtsa ba'i phye ma ra gcin gyis lan mang du bsgos la /
T16TD4434E:272a-2: rtsa bas dang lhan cig tu btags te btsags pa snar blugs na yang dug gis sems nyams par byas pa las slar dran par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:272a-7: ko sha ta ka'i 'bras bu rnams kyi phye ma ba gcin dang lhan cig tu btags te btsags pa ni dug sman gyi mchog yin te /
T16TD4434E:272a-8: btung ba la sogs pa byas na dug sel bar byed do //
T16TD4434E:272a-19: dug mo nyung gi shun lpags dang /
T16TD4434E:272a-20: aarka rnams sbyar ba yang dug sman chen po yin no //
T16TD4434E:272a-30: pi pi ling rnams sbyar ba yang dug sman yin te /
T16TD4434E:272a-32: sku ba ro kha ba'i sa bon ba lang gi mkhris pa dang lhan cig tu btags pa 'di ni tshangs pa'i dug sman zhes bya ste btung ba la sogs pa byas na dug thams cad sel to //
T16TD4434E:272a-33: shi ri shi'i rtsa ba dang /
T16TD4434E:272a-37: sa bon rnam pa 'di lnga ba gcin dang lhan cig tu btags pa'i sman 'di yang dug sel ba yin no //
T16TD4434E:272a-45: ha re nu ka rnams kyi phye ma sbrang rtsi dang sbyar ba 'di yang dug sman yin te /
T16TD4434E:272a-47: brgyal ba las slar dran par byed pa la sogs pa'i las thams cad byed do //
T16TD4434E:272a-48: lan tshva rnam pa lnga dang /
T16TD4434E:272b-0: btsod rnams kyi phye ma sbrang rtsi dang sbyar ba'i dug @272b sman dva'i nang du bzhag pa yang las thams cad byed pa yin no //
T16TD4434E:272b-22: gandha pri yam ku rnams kyi phye ma sbyar ba'i dug sman gyi ming ni /
T16TD4434E:272b-23: zla shar zhes bya ste dug thams cad 'joms par byed do //
T16TD4434E:272b-37: aa pa ra dzi ta dang /
T16TD4434E:272b-39: shing mngar rnams kyi phye ma ba gcin dang lhan cig btags pa'i dug sman 'di'i ming ni /
T16TD4434E:272b-49: yang na re re yang rung ste dug gsod pa'i mchog yin no //
T16TD4434E:272b-50: rgya skyegs shing gi thal ba pa chu dang sbyar te btsags la dri ma dang snyigs ma bor ba'i nang du /
T16TD4434E:272b-63: byi dang ga dang rgyam tsha rnams kyi phye ma bskol te gzar bu la chags su btub pa tsam du tshos nas /
T16TD4434E:272b-64: rva'i nang du bzhag pa las nang re bzhin rgya shug gi 'brum bu tsam re re 'bras ba krus pa'i khu ba'am /
T16TD4434E:272b-65: 'o ma'am char pa'i chu gang yang rung ba dang sbyar te 'thungs na dug gi mthu chen po yang sel cing /
T16TD4434E:273a-4: rims rnams med par byed do //
T16TD4434E:273a-6: ba lang gi gci ba'i khu ba sprang rtsi dang sbyar ba'i skyug sman blud de skyug tu gzhug go /
T16TD4434E:273a-7: dug sman gyi sbyor ba mang po rnams las gang gtang yang rung ste /
T16TD4434E:273a-8: thog mar snying la dug mi 'dzin par bsrung ba'i phyir smyur te mar blud par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:273a-10: mda' dug can gyis rmas pa la ni /
T16TD4434E:273a-13: sbrang rtsi rnams sbyar ba'i mar mchog tu bzang ste btung bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:273a-15: gser gyi phye ma khar dang sbrang rtsis sbyar ba'i lde gu zos na dug sbyar ma shin tu drag po thams cad kyang zhi bar byed do //
T16TD4434E:273a-16: sdig pas zin pa la ni shing t'a la'i lo ma dang /
T16TD4434E:273a-19: ras rnying pa rnams mar dang sbyar te bsregs pa'i dud pa'am /
T16TD4434E:273a-20: yang na rma bya'i sgro 'o ma dang sbyar te bsregs pa'i dud pas bdugs par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:273a-21: yang na pa la sha'i sa bon shing aarka'i 'o ma dang lhan gcig btags pa'i lde khu dang /
T16TD4434E:273a-22: yang na pi pi ling dang shi ri sha'i 'bras bu sbyar ba'i lde gus rma khar skus na sdig pa'i dug gis nyam thag pa sel to //
T16TD4434E:273a-27: bca' sga rnams kyi phye ma ba lang gi lci ba'i khu ba dang sbyar te btang la ri lu byas pa yang sdig pa'i dug gis nyam thag pa sel to //
T16TD4434E:273a-28: byi ba'i sos zin pa'i dug la ni /
T16TD4434E:273a-31: ti la ka'i rtsa ba dang /
T16TD4434E:273a-32: gi ka rni ka'i rtsa ba rnams gyi phye ma khar dang /
T16TD4434E:273a-35: sbyar te 'thung na byi bas zin pa'i dug sel to //
T16TD4434E:273a-36: yang na byi bas zin pa'i dug la /
T16TD4434E:273a-37: ha tsa ra'i rtsa ba'i phye ma dang /
T16TD4434E:273a-38: sbrang rtsi 'bras bkrus pa'i khu ba dang sbyar ba'am /
T16TD4434E:273a-39: yang na ti la ka'i me tog gam lo ma gang yang rung ba 'o ma dang /
T16TD4434E:273b-0: lhan cig tu btags te btung bar @273b bya'o //
T16TD4434E:273b-2: ne'u le'i sha gang yang rung ba btsos pa'i khu ba 'thungs na /
T16TD4434E:273b-3: byi bas zin pa'i dug bla gnyan gyi nad dang bcas pa yang myur du sel to //
T16TD4434E:273b-4: khyi smyon gyis zos pa la ni /
T16TD4434E:273b-5: shing aa ko ta'i yal ga'i thor to dang rtsa ba bskol te gdus pa'i khu ba srang gsum gyi nang du zhun mar srang gcig btab ste 'thungs na khyi smyon gyis zin pa'i dug sel to //
T16TD4434E:273b-7: til btags pa'i phye ma shing aarka'i 'o ma dang til mar gyis sbyar te 'thungs na khyi so gdug pas zin pa'i dug 'tsho dka' ba yang myur du sel bar byed do //
T16TD4434E:273b-8: srog chags phra mo'o cog gis zin pa'i dug sman ni /
T16TD4434E:273b-9: nas tshig 'khus pa'i thal ba dang /
T16TD4434E:273b-19: ru rta rnams kyi phye ma 'bras bkrus pa'i khu par btab cing bsku bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:273b-20: shing nye rong gi rtsa ba dang /
T16TD4434E:273b-21: mon sne'u dmar ru'i phye ma cha bsnyams te /
T16TD4434E:273b-22: mar dang sbyar ba 'thungs na yang srog chags phra mo thams cad kyi dug shin tu mthu che ba yang myur du sel lo //
T16TD4434E:273b-23: yang phug ron gyi rtug pa dang /
T16TD4434E:273b-28: le brgan rtsi'i sa bon dang /
T16TD4434E:273b-31: karni kar rnams sbyar ba yang srog chags phra mo'i dug sel ba'i mchog yin no //
T16TD4434E:273b-40: she lu rnams sbyar ba ni srog chags phra mos kha dug go cog gi dug sel ba'i sman yin no //
T16TD4434E:273b-45: pu na rna ba rnam gnyis dang /
T16TD4434E:274a-0: 'di rnams sbyar ba yang srog chags phra mos kha dug go cog gi dug thams cad @274a * //
T16TD4434E:274a-2: sdig pas zin pa'i dug ma gtogs pa dug gis nyam thag pa gzhan thams cad la ni /
T16TD4434E:274a-4: sman la sogs pa bsil ba'i cho ga rnams bya'o //
T16TD4434E:274a-5: dug gis phog go cog la khro ba dang /
T16TD4434E:274a-8: nyal po rnams byar mi rung ngo //
T16TD4434E:274a-9: dug gis phog pa las rims la sogs pa'i bla gnyan gyi nad gzhan gyis thebs pa rnams la ni so so'i sman gang yin pa smyur te gso bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:274a-10: dug gis nyam thag ba rnams la kha zas kyang tsha ba bskyad par mi 'gyur ba rnams bza' zhing btung bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:274a-11: dug gso ba'i rgyud kyi le'u ste nyi shu rtsa bdun pa rdzogs so /
T16TD4434E:274a-13: // / de nas sman bcud kyis len dang /
T16TD4434E:274a-14: ro tsa bar bya ba'i rgyud kyi le'u bshad par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:274a-15: de la sman gang skra dkar ba dang /
T16TD4434E:274a-16: na ba med bar byed ba de ni bcud kyis len zhes bya ba yin no //
T16TD4434E:274a-19: yang na bar ma'i tshe bsgrub par bya ste /
T16TD4434E:274a-22: khrus la sogs pas lus kyi phyi nang dag par byas nas brtsam par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:274a-23: de la sgrub pa'i thabs ni /
T16TD4434E:274a-27: skyu ru ra'i 'bras bu'i phye ma rnams sbyar pas bum pa bkang la /
T16TD4434E:274a-28: lo phyed kyi bar du nas kyi dkyil du bzhag pa las rgyun tu bran par zos na /
T16TD4434E:274a-29: skra dkar por gyur pa med par byed do //
T16TD4434E:274a-30: yang na aa ru ra dang /
T16TD4434E:274a-34: kha ra rnams kyi phye ma dang /
T16TD4434E:274a-35: lcags kyi phye ma rnams mar dang til mar dang sbyar te zos na rgas pas mi tshugs so //
T16TD4434E:274a-39: lcags byi bye ma rnams sbrang rtsi dang /
T16TD4434E:274a-41: til mar rnams dang sbyar ba ji ste mis zos nas gzhon nur gyur pa de ni ngo mtshar mi che'o //
T16TD4434E:274a-44: pi pi ling rnams kyi phye ma dang /
T16TD4434E:274b-0: @274b lcags kyi phye ma rnams mar dang /
T16TD4434E:274b-2: sbrang rtsi rnams dang sbyar te rgyun tu zos na yang rgas pa dang /
T16TD4434E:274b-3: skra dkar por gyur pa sel to //
T16TD4434E:274b-7: pi pi ling rnams kyi phye ma dang /
T16TD4434E:274b-9: til mar rnams 'bras bu gsum bskol ba'i khu ba'i nang du blugs te /
T16TD4434E:274b-10: gzar bu la chags su btub pa tsam du bskol ba yang sman bcud kyis len du 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:274b-11: lcags glebs te dmar por bsregs la 'bras bu gsum bskol ba'i khu ba bsgrangs pa'i nang du smyug cing khol bcad par bya ba de lta bur lan mang du byas pa'i lcags te se brdar gyis brdar ba'i phye ma sbrang rtsi dang mar dang sbyar te zos na yang tshe ring bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:274b-12: yang na skyu ru ra bskol ba'i khu ba dang /
T16TD4434E:274b-13: mar sbrang rtsi rnams cha bsnyams te srang brgya brgya dang /
T16TD4434E:274b-14: lcags kyi phye ma srang nyis brgya dang /
T16TD4434E:274b-15: 'di rnams sbyar ba lcags kyi snod du blugs te bzhag pa yang tshe ring bar byed pa'i mchog yin no //
T16TD4434E:274b-17: 'bras bu gsum gyi phye ma dang /
T16TD4434E:274b-18: sbrang rtsi dang sbyar te zos na yang /
T16TD4434E:274b-19: gshin rje'i snga ltas skra dkar por gyur ba med par byad do //
T16TD4434E:274b-20: byi dang ga'i phye ma dang /
T16TD4434E:274b-23: lcags kyi phye ma rnams cha bsnyams te sbyar ba bum pa'i nang du blugs la /
T16TD4434E:274b-24: mon sran sde'u'i dkyil du bzhag pa las ran par zos na /
T16TD4434E:274b-25: skra mthing gar 'gyur zhing stobs dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:274b-26: tam pa la phye ma srang brgya dang /
T16TD4434E:274b-28: sbrang rtsi srang brgya sbyar te zla ba gcig gi bar du snod kyi nang du bzhag pa las /
T16TD4434E:274b-29: rgyun tu zos la kha zas 'o ma dang ldan par zos na skra dkar po med par byed cing zla ba bzhin du mdzes par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:274b-30: sman par hi'i rtsa ba'i phye ma srang brgya sbrang rtsi dang sbyar te /
T16TD4434E:274b-31: mthar gyis za zhing 'o mas phul la kha zas 'o ma dang mar dang ldan par za zhing /
T16TD4434E:274b-32: nan tan du byas na lang tsho dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:275a-0: yang na zla ba gcig gi bar du sman ba ra hi zhib tu btags pa'i phye ma sbrang @275a * //
T16TD4434E:275a-1: rtsi dang sbyar ba'i lde gu zos la /
T16TD4434E:275a-2: de'i 'og tu bar hi'i phye ma 'o ma dang bskol te bsgrangs la btsags pa 'thungs na yang sman bcud kyi len du 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:275a-3: pu na rna ba'i rtsa ba zhib tu btags pa'i phye ma srang phyed 'o ma bskol te phyung ba'i nang du btab ste zla ba gnyis sam lo gcig gi bar du rgyun du 'thungs na yang rga ba med par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:275a-12: bya ghri rnams kyang re re nas bu na rna ba'i cho ga gong du bshad pa bzhin du byas na /
T16TD4434E:275a-13: yon tan de bzhin du 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:275a-14: sha skye bar 'dod pa la ni /
T16TD4434E:275a-15: zla ba phyed kyi bar du /
T16TD4434E:275a-16: sman aa sho gandha'i phye ma /
T16TD4434E:275a-19: chu bskol ba dron mo rnams las gang yang rung ba dang sbyar te 'thungs nas kha zas 'phrod pa bza' bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:275a-20: sman bcud kyis len sgrub par 'dod pa rnams kyis ni /
T16TD4434E:275a-21: rtag tu kha zas 'bras zhag drug cus smin pa'i chan 'o ma dang /
T16TD4434E:275a-22: mon sran sde'u'i khu bcud dang /
T16TD4434E:275a-24: ri dags skams na gnas pa'i sha khu rnams las gang yang rung ba dang bsreg cing bza' bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:275a-25: ro tsa bar bya ba'i cho ga ni /
T16TD4434E:275a-26: shing mngar gyi phye ma zho gnyis mar dang sbrang rtsi dang sbyar te /
T16TD4434E:275a-27: rtag tu zos la de'i rjes la 'o ma 'thungs na rgan po yang ro tsa bar byed do //
T16TD4434E:275a-28: mon sran sde'u srang re re cho ga gong ma ltar byas na yang de bzhin du 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:275a-31: khar rnams kyi phye ma 'o ma dang sbyar ba'am /
T16TD4434E:275a-32: yang na sman autstsha de'i phye ma khar dang /
T16TD4434E:275a-33: 'o ma dang sbyar ba 'thungs na yang /
T16TD4434E:275a-35: byi da ra'i phye ma de nyid kyi khu bas lan mang du bsgos pa btags te /
T16TD4434E:275a-36: mar dang sbrang rtsi dang sbyar ba'i lde gus ni shin tu ro tsa bar bshad do //

T16TD4434E:275b-2: yang na mon sran sde'u shun lpags bshus te zhib tu btags pa'i phye ma 'o ma dang mar gyi nang du bskol te /

T16TD4434E:275b-21: // / de nas byis pa'i rgyud kyi le'u bshad par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:275b-22: de la bud med ni dga' bar bya ste /

T16TD4434E:275b-27: de la rlung las gyur pa'i mo mtshan gyi nad kyi mtshan ma ni /
T16TD4434E:275b-32: phal phal byed pa rnams yin no //
T16TD4434E:275b-33: mkhris pa 'khrugs pa'i mtshan ma las gyur pa ni /

T16TD4434E:275b-37: bad kan 'khrugs pa las gyur pa'i mo mtshan g-yeng ba dang /

T16TD4434E:276a-1: las gyur pa'i mo mtshan gyi nad gso ba'i cho ga ni /
T16TD4434E:276a-3: mon sran sde'u'i chan gyi dugs sam /

T16TD4434E:276a-5: mdor na rlung las gyur pa'i mo mtshan gyi nad la ni /

T16TD4434E:276a-9: yang na mo mtshan gyi nad la ni /

T16TD4434E:276a-12: yang na pi pi ling dang /

T16TD4434E:276a-15: pha bong gi dreg pa dang /

T16TD4434E:276a-28: mkhris pa las gyur pa'i mo mtshan gyi nang la yang bzang la /

T16TD4434E:276a-30: mkhris pa 'khrugs pa las gyur pa'i mo mtshan gyi nad la ni /

T16TD4434E:276b-6: skyes pa'i khu ba nyung la bud med kyi khrag mang na ni bu mor 'gyur ro //

T16TD4434E:276b-9: rgyam tsha 'am shing pa ta'i yal ga'am rtse mo gang yang rung ba'i phye ma 'o ma dang btags te btsags pa'i khu ba las thigs pa bzhi ma nyal ba'i snga rol tu bud med kyi sna g-yon par blugs na khye'ur 'gyur ro //

T16TD4434E:279b-12: na ma sta ma ba ka ya /
T16TD4434E:279b-13: satya satya ta nu te sv'a h'a /
T16TD4434E:279b-14: byis ba'i rgyud kyi le'u ste nyi shu dgu pa rdzogs so /
T16TD4434E:279b-16: // / de nas las rnam lnga'i le'u bshad par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:279b-21: bkru sman drag po mas btang ba dang /
T16TD4434E:279b-22: 'jam rtsi mas btang ba rnams yin par shes par bya ste /
T16TD4434E:279b-23: de dag gi cho ga bshad par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:279b-24: de la skyug sman mas btang ba'i thabs ni /
T16TD4434E:279b-25: thog mar sman pas nad pa la mar dang /
T16TD4434E:279b-26: til mar la sogs pa snum bag gang yang rung ba'i 'jam rtsi blud la /
T16TD4434E:279b-27: de'i 'og tu dugs rnam lnga zhes bya ba khyim dron por lus me sa bsro ba dang /
T16TD4434E:279b-28: rdo bsregs pa'i steng du chu blugs pa'i rlangs pas bdug cing rdul gdon pa dang /
T16TD4434E:279b-29: nyi tshan gyis bdug pa dang /
T16TD4434E:279b-30: dugs kyi sman bsros pa'i phur mas dugs bya ba dang /
T16TD4434E:279b-32: rdo la sogs pa bsros pa'i dugs rnam pa 'di lnga gang yang rung bas lus legs par dros par byas nas gos dron po bskon te /
T16TD4434E:279b-34: rkub rten pus mor phyin tsam gyi steng du 'dug ste /
T16TD4434E:279b-36: bya sgro la sogs pa 'jam pos gre ba nas dkrug cing skyug tu gzhug go //
T16TD4434E:279b-40: rgyam tsha rnams kyi phye ma dang /
T16TD4434E:279b-42: shing mngar bskol ba'i khu ba dang sbyar ba 'di ni skyug sman gyi mchog yin te /
T16TD4434E:280a-0: @280a * // dron por 'og dros kyis gzung ste blud la skyug tu gzhug go / yang na sbyar dug ces bya ba /
T16TD4434E:280a-2: mon sran sde'u gsum bsregs pa'i thug ba /
T16TD4434E:280a-5: yang na po son cha'i sa bon 'o ma dang sbyar te bskol ba 'am /
T16TD4434E:280a-6: yang na pi pi ling la sogs pa'i skyug sman sbrang rtsi dang ldan pa gong du smos pa rnams po son cha'i 'bras bu lnga bskol ba'i khu ba dang sbyar te dron por 'thungs na snying tshim par skyugs par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:280a-7: ku ba ro kha ba dang /
T16TD4434E:280a-9: dug mo nyung gi 'bras bu dang /
T16TD4434E:280a-11: dha marga ba rnams kyang skyug sman yin te /
T16TD4434E:280a-12: so sor po son cha dang 'dra bar sbyar ro //
T16TD4434E:280a-13: de nas skyugs pa'i rjes la /
T16TD4434E:280a-17: mgo bo yang bar gyur na skyug sman legs pa yin no //
T16TD4434E:280a-19: skyug sman ma legs pa yin par bshad do //
T16TD4434E:280a-20: skyug pa'i tshod ma rig ste drags na nad du 'gyur te /
T16TD4434E:280a-25: dran pa nyams shing myos pa dang /
T16TD4434E:280a-27: khrag skyugs pa rnams las rtogs par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:280a-29: bad kan las gyur pa'i nad dang /
T16TD4434E:280a-35: bsud pa rnams la nyams stobs dang sbyar te gtang bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:280a-36: mig nad rab rib yod pa dang /
T16TD4434E:280a-40: rtug skam gyi nad kyis nyam thag pa dang /
T16TD4434E:280a-43: skya rbab kyi nad yod pa rnams la ni /
T16TD4434E:280a-44: skyug sman du btang du mi rung ngo //
T16TD4434E:280a-45: bkru sman btang ba'i thabs ni /
T16TD4434E:280a-46: thog mar mar dang til mar la sogs pa snum bag gang yang rung ba'i 'jam rtsi blud la /
T16TD4434E:280b-0: de'i 'og tu sngar bshad pa @280b bzhin du dugs kyis lus bsros te skyug sman btang la /
T16TD4434E:280b-2: bkru sman btang ba'i thabs de ltar ma byas te cho ga log par byas na pho ba'i nad skyed par bshad do //
T16TD4434E:280b-3: de la mkhris pa'i rang bzhin can gyi mi ni lto snyi'o //
T16TD4434E:280b-4: rlung dang bad kan gyi rang bzhin can gyi mi ni lto sra ba yin no //
T16TD4434E:280b-5: nad gzhi rnams stobs mnyam pa'i lto ni 'bring ste /
T16TD4434E:280b-6: de dag la sman gyi tshod ci rigs par dpag cing gtang bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:280b-7: de la rlung las gyur pa'i nad kyis nyam thag pa'i mi la bkru sman btang ba'i thabs ni /
T16TD4434E:280b-11: sga rnams kyi phye ma rtsabs skyur po'am /
T16TD4434E:280b-13: ri dags skams na gnas pa'i sha'i khu ba gang yang rung ba dang sbyar te btung bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:280b-14: mkhris pa las gyur pa'i nad yod pa la ni /
T16TD4434E:280b-15: shing nye rong phye ma sman ro mngar ba dang /
T16TD4434E:280b-16: kha ba la sogs pa mkhris pa'i nad la phan pa'i sman gang yang rung ba bskol ba'i khu ba dang sbyar ba'i bkru sman gtang bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:280b-17: bad kan las gyur pa'i nad kyis gnod par gyur pa la ni /
T16TD4434E:280b-18: 'bras bu gsum bskol ba'i khu ba tsha ba gsum gyi phye ma dang ba gcin gyis sbyar ba'i bkru sman gtang bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:280b-22: nas tshig 'khus pa'i thal ba rnams kyi phye ma sbrang rtsi dang sbyar ba'i lde gu 'di ni bad kan las gyur pa'i nad do cog gi bkru sman gyi mchog yin te bza' bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:280b-25: pi pi ling rnams kyi phye ma chur bskol ba'i khu ba dron po dang sbyar ba'i bkru sman lcags mda' zhes bya ba 'di ni nad do cog sel ba'i bkru sman gyi mchog yin te btung bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:280b-27: shing nye rong gi phye ma srang gcig dang /
T16TD4434E:280b-28: pi pi ling gi phye ma zho gnyis te 'di rnams sbrang rtsi dang sbyar ba'i lde gu'i bkru sman las ren par zos na yang nad do cog sel to //
T16TD4434E:281a-2: shing dong rnams kyi phye ma dang /
T16TD4434E:281a-3: dri sna gsum zhes bya ba shing cha dang /
T16TD4434E:281a-5: gandha ba tra rnams kyi phye ma btab la /
T16TD4434E:281a-7: gong bur bsgongs ba'i bkru sman gyis kyang nad do cog sel to /
T16TD4434E:281a-8: dmu rdzings la sogs pa la ni /
T16TD4434E:281a-11: shing snu ha'i lo mas lan mang du bsgos la /
T16TD4434E:281a-12: bu mar dang sbrang rtsi sbyar te dri sna gsum gyis btab pa'i lde gu'i bkru sman btang ngo //
T16TD4434E:281a-17: mdangs gsal bar gyur na bkru sman legs pa yin no //
T16TD4434E:281a-19: lus la thig le khra bor byung ba dang /
T16TD4434E:281a-20: lus lci bar gyur ba rnams ni bkru sman ma legs pa'i mtshan mar shes par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:281a-21: bkru sman drags pa'i mtshan ma ni /
T16TD4434E:281a-27: sha rjen bkrus pa'i khu ba 'dra ba mthur du 'byung ba rnams yin no //
T16TD4434E:281a-33: dreg dang skya sbab kyi nad yod pa rnams la gtang bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:281a-34: zad kyi nad yod pa dang /
T16TD4434E:281a-36: bud med sgrum ma rnams la ni bkru sman btang du mi rung ngo //
T16TD4434E:281a-37: skyug sman btang ba las ha cang mang du skyug cing 'chad du mi btub pa la ni /
T16TD4434E:281a-38: sman pas bkru sman zhim zhing yid gar 'ong ba las chung zad tsam byin na skyug pa 'chad par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:281a-39: bkru sman btang ba las ha cang mang du 'khru zhing 'chad du mi btub pa la ni skyug sman cung zad btab na 'chad par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:281a-40: bkru sman ha cang drags pa ni /
T16TD4434E:281a-44: can dan rnams kyis lus byugs pa dang /
T16TD4434E:281a-45: lus blugs pa dang btung ba rnams bya'o //
T16TD4434E:281a-46: sman snar blugs pa zhes bya ba ni /
T16TD4434E:281b-1: til mar ram sman snar blugs pa yin te /
T16TD4434E:281b-2: de yang mar ram til mar nyi tshe snar blugs pa dang /
T16TD4434E:281b-3: sman mar ram sman gyi til mar blugs shing /
T16TD4434E:281b-4: bad kan dang chu ser sna nas drang ba dang /
T16TD4434E:281b-5: snum gyis sna'i nang du bsku ba dang /
T16TD4434E:281b-6: sman gyi phur ma sna sgor btsir zhing blugs pa dang /
T16TD4434E:281b-7: sman gyi phye ma lce'i nang du blugs te /
T16TD4434E:281b-9: rnam pa lnga yod par shes par bya ste /
T16TD4434E:281b-10: sman snar blugs pa'i rnam grangs de dag btang ba'i thabs ni /
T16TD4434E:281b-12: zan ma zos pa'i snga rol du lag pa gnyis drag du drud pa'i drod kyis /
T16TD4434E:281b-14: gdong thams cad legs par mnye zhing bsros la /
T16TD4434E:281b-15: kha sna dang mtshul ba'i dri ma thams cad dag par bsal nas mgo smad de gtang bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:281b-16: sman snar blugs pa'i cho ga byed pa des mgo bkru ba dang /
T16TD4434E:281b-19: nyin par gnyid log pa la sogs pa mi rung ba rnams spang bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:281b-20: de la mar dang til mar snar blugs pa'i tshod ni thigs pa brgyad dam /
T16TD4434E:281b-21: yad na mdzub mo'i tshigs pa gnyis phan chad lan gcig smyugs pal [?] ci chags pa snar blugs so //
T16TD4434E:281b-23: srang phyed snar blugs pa yin no //
T16TD4434E:281b-24: tshad rnam gcig ni nyams stobs che chung las dpags te thigs pa bzhi 'am drug gam brgyad blugs par bya ste /
T16TD4434E:281b-25: tshad kyi sna grangs mang po bstan pa 'di kun kyang nad pa'i nyams stobs che chung dang sbyar zhing gtang bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:281b-27: til mar snar blugs shing bad kan dang chu ser sna nas drang ba ni nam tshong yan chad kyi nad rnams la btang ba yin no /
T16TD4434E:281b-29: // / da ni sman mar gyi 'jam rtsi dang /
T16TD4434E:281b-30: bcung mas btang ba'i cho ga bshad nge [*de?]/
T16TD4434E:281b-31: sman mas btang ba'i dpyad ni /
T16TD4434E:281b-32: lcags dang zangs la sogs pa gang yang rung ba las byas pa'i gce'u srid sor bcu gnyis pa la /
T16TD4434E:282a-0: gnag gi mjug snying gi dbyibs bzhin du byin gyis phra zhing zlum @282a * //
T16TD4434E:282a-2: rtsa ba sboms pa ni the bong shong tsam du bya /
T16TD4434E:282a-3: thor to phra mo ni srin shong tsam la 'jam por byas te /
T16TD4434E:282a-4: thor to phra mo logs nas sor gsum gyi tshu rol du phang lo tsam zhig gags byas la /
T16TD4434E:282a-5: rtsa ba spom po logs kyi khar yang sman blugs pa'i snod gnag gi lgang pa bzang po dam por gdags shing /
T16TD4434E:282a-6: lgang pa mi 'bud pa'i gags ci ran pa kha gnyis su bcad la de'i bar du lgang pa'i kha bcing bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:282a-7: de nas sman btang ba'i tshe sngar kha zas zos nas glo g-yon phyogs kyis nyal la /
T16TD4434E:282a-8: rkang pa g-yon pa ni brkyang /
T16TD4434E:282a-10: gzhang kha dang lce'u snum gyis byugs la /
T16TD4434E:282a-12: rgyam tsha'i phye ma mar ram til mar dang /
T16TD4434E:282a-13: chu dang ldan par bskol la /
T16TD4434E:282a-14: mar nyi tshe lus pa btsags pa'am /
T16TD4434E:282a-18: srang bzhi mi nyid kyi nyams stobs dang sbyar zhing tshod ran pa dang /
T16TD4434E:282a-19: dron por mas btang zhing gce'u 'i rtse mo nang du bcug la /
T16TD4434E:282a-20: gags la thug par byas te /
T16TD4434E:282a-21: lag pa g-yon pas gce'u'i sked pa nas dam du bzung zhing lgang pa'i nang du rlung ma song bar byas te /
T16TD4434E:282a-22: ha cang mi drag mi ngal ba dang /
T16TD4434E:282a-23: bar du mi gda' mi bcad cing /
T16TD4434E:282a-24: rgyun chags par lan gcig gis rdzogs par lag pa g-yas pas lgang pa btsir la rlung nang du mi 'gro bar bya ba'i phyir sman gyi lhag ma chung zad tsam lus par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:282a-25: sman btang zin nas gan rgyal du bsnyal te /
T16TD4434E:282a-26: rkang lag bzhi char gyen du bteg la lan gsum gyi bar du drag tu brkyang zhing bskum pa byas nas /
T16TD4434E:282a-28: bdag nyid kyi rting pas rkub tshos la lan gnyis gsum du brdabs la /
T16TD4434E:282a-29: de'i 'og tu mi gzhan gyis rkang pa'i mthil du khu tshur gyis lan gnyis gsum du brdegs nas /
T16TD4434E:282b-0: ro smad stod de nyal du gzhug go / sman mar gyi cho ga 'di ni zhag lon gyi bar du 'khyil te phyir ma byung yang mi @282b rung bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:282b-1: de bas kyang yun ring du phyir 'byung du ma btub na /
T16TD4434E:282b-2: phyi sa 'gags pa'i cho ga sngar bstan pa bzhin du /
T16TD4434E:282b-3: sman gyi reng bu mas gzhug pa'am /
T16TD4434E:282b-4: yang na bkru sman 'jam pos myur du dbyung zhing sbyang bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:282b-5: ji ste phyir ma byung yang mi bde ba'am lci ba'i bag med cing /
T16TD4434E:282b-6: tha mal bar 'dug pa la ni bkru sman la sogs pa btang mi dgos te /
T16TD4434E:282b-7: chu bskol ba'i dron po 'thungs pas kyang 'byung bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:282b-8: de la mar dang phyi sa 'dres par 'byung ba ni sman legs pa'i mtshan ma yin no //
T16TD4434E:282b-9: phyi sa ma 'dres par mar nyi tshe 'byung ba dang lus tsha bar gyur pa ni sman ma legs pa'i mtshan ma yin no //
T16TD4434E:282b-10: mar ni ma byung la phyi sa ni tha mal par byung la /
T16TD4434E:282b-11: lto mi bde ba'i bag tu ma gyur na yang me'i drod che bas sman khong du zhu bar gyur pa yin te mi rung ba med do //
T16TD4434E:282b-12: kha zas ni sman btang nas nam bkres par gyur na /
T16TD4434E:282b-13: gdod yang zhing 'phrod pa'i bag las bza'o /
T16TD4434E:282b-14: sman mas btang nas ring po ma lon par phyir byung na sman don du ma gyur ba yin te /
T16TD4434E:282b-15: yang na cho ga snga ma bzhin du bzlas te gtang bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:282b-16: de la sman mar gyi 'jam rtsi'i bcud mas btang ba dang /
T16TD4434E:282b-17: bkru sman drag po mas btang ba gnyi ga yang rlung nad kyi bag yod pa la gtong bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:282b-23: dmu rdzings yod pa la sogs pa la ni gtang du mi rung ngo //
T16TD4434E:282b-24: bkru sman drag po mas btang ba'i cho ga ni sngar zhag gnyis gsum gyi snga rol du sman mar gyi 'jam rtsims btang la bkru sran drag po nyid mas btang ba'i nyin par nyi ma dron po la snga dro nas lus snum gyis byug cing mnye ba dang /
T16TD4434E:282b-25: dugs sna tshogs kyis lus shin tu dros shing sha grol bar byas la /
T16TD4434E:282b-26: nang par nas kha zas kyi bag mi bza' mi btung bar nyi ma phyed yol tsam na sman mas gtang bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:283a-0: de la btang ba'i thabs ni gan rkyal du bsnyal la sman mar gyi bcud mas btang ba bzhin du @283a * //
T16TD4434E:283a-1: gce'u dang lgang par sbyar nas sman ha cang mi tsha ha cang mi grang bar dron par byas te lgang pa lag bas btsir la /
T16TD4434E:283a-2: ha cang mi drag mi ngal ba dang /
T16TD4434E:283a-3: bar du mi gda' mi bcad par rgyun chags par lan gcig gis rdzogs par btang ngo //
T16TD4434E:283a-4: dri ma byung ba'i snod dam /
T16TD4434E:283a-5: khung bu yang snga nas drung du bsnyen la /
T16TD4434E:283a-6: sems gud du mi g-yeng bar sman lto na 'dug pa rnams 'byung la thug go snyam du bsam pa gtad par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:283a-7: de la dbyung ba'i tshod ni /
T16TD4434E:283a-8: sman mas btang nas yi ge'i 'bru sum cu drag dal ran tsam du brjod cing zin tsam na 'byung ba'i rigs te /
T16TD4434E:283a-9: tha mal pa tsog cog por 'dug la dbyung bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:283a-10: de nas nad ma phyin tam /
T16TD4434E:283a-11: ma zhag par gyur na bsnan bzod dang mi bzod mi'i nyams stobs las dpags te /
T16TD4434E:283a-12: bzod pa 'dra na snga ma bzhin du lan gnyis lan gsum gyi bar du bsnan te bkrus nas /
T16TD4434E:283a-13: de'i 'og tu chu dron pos khrus byas la /
T16TD4434E:283a-14: kha zas sha khu dang ldan pa bzang po zos nas /
T16TD4434E:283a-15: de'i rjes la lus rlung 'jug pa lta na /
T16TD4434E:283a-16: de'i mod la mar gyi 'jam rtsi'i bcud mas btang ba cho ga sngar bshad pa bzhin du ba'o //
T16TD4434E:283a-17: 'phral du rlung 'jug pa'i dogs pa med na /
T16TD4434E:283a-18: zhag gnyis sam gsum gyis bcad de /
T16TD4434E:283a-19: gdod mar gyi 'jam rtsi'i bcud mas btang ngo //
T16TD4434E:283a-20: bkru sman drag po khong du btang ba des ma byung na /
T16TD4434E:283a-23: lto spo ba la sogs pa'i nad mang por 'gyur te /
T16TD4434E:283a-24: nyen che bas na de la ni /
T16TD4434E:283a-25: du 'byung ran pa'i dus las yol ma thag tu 'jam rtsi snon po mas btang ba dang /
T16TD4434E:283a-27: skrag par bya ba la sogs pa'i cho ga byas na bzang ngo //
T16TD4434E:283a-28: bkru sman drag po mas btang ba'i cho ga 'di ni phan yon che zhing nyen yang chebs na gya tshom du btang du mi rung ste /
T16TD4434E:283a-29: cho ga de la mkhas pa'i sman pa mang po tshogs pas legs par dpyad cing gtang bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:283b-0: de la bkru sman drag pa mas btang @283b ba la ni /
T16TD4434E:283b-1: sman gyi khu bsrang drug dang /
T16TD4434E:283b-2: mar ram til mar cha gcig dang /
T16TD4434E:283b-3: sman gyi phye ma srang gsum dang /
T16TD4434E:283b-5: sbrang rtsi ci ran pa dang /
T16TD4434E:283b-6: 'di rnams ni spyi'i cho ga yin te /
T16TD4434E:283b-10: bad kan gang gi sman du btang ba las /
T16TD4434E:283b-11: de dag so so'i sman 'og nas 'gyung ba bzhin du bsnan te /
T16TD4434E:283b-12: skam gsher spyir srang nyi shu rtsa bzhi byung bar grangs bkang zhing cho ga 'og nas rgyas par 'byung ba bzhin du sbyar ro //
T16TD4434E:283b-13: de la rlung nad bsal ba'i bkru sman drag po mas btang ba ni /
T16TD4434E:283b-14: rlung sel ba'i sman gang yin pa rnams bskol ba'i khu ba dang /
T16TD4434E:283b-15: shing nye rong gi phye ma dang /
T16TD4434E:283b-16: rgyam tsha bro ba tsam dang /
T16TD4434E:283b-17: rtsabs skyur po rnams lhan cig tu sbyar te dron por btang ngo //
T16TD4434E:283b-18: rgya shug la sogs pa'i sde tshan dang /
T16TD4434E:283b-21: la phug skam po rnams las sna re re yang srang gnyis gnyis lhan cig tu chu phul gang la srang brgyad du brtsis pa chu phul drug cu rtsa bzhi'i nang du bskol te /
T16TD4434E:283b-22: chu'i brgyad cha gcig lus pa btsags pa dang /
T16TD4434E:283b-28: gla sgang rnams kyi phye ma sbrang rtsi dang /
T16TD4434E:283b-29: rtsabs skyur po dang ba gcin rnams sbyar ba'i bkru sman drag po mas btang ba yang rlung nad sel bar byed do //
T16TD4434E:283b-30: mkhris pa bsal ba'i bkru sman drag po mas btang ba'i sman ni ;
T16TD4434E:283b-31: shing n+ya gro dha la sogs pa'i sde tshan bskol ba'i khu ba dang /
T16TD4434E:283b-32: bu tshang rto la sogs pa'i sde tshan btags pa'i phye ma dang /
T16TD4434E:283b-35: kha ra rnams sbyar ba btang na mkhris pa sel to //
T16TD4434E:283b-36: bad kan sel ba'i bkru sman drag po mas btang ba'i sman ni /
T16TD4434E:283b-37: dong ga la sogs pa'i sde tshan bskol ba'i khu ba dang /
T16TD4434E:283b-38: pi pi ling la sogs pa'i sde tshan btags pa'i phye ma dang /
T16TD4434E:283b-39: ba gcin dang sbrang rtsi rnams sbyar te btang na bad kan sel to //
T16TD4434E:284a-10: po son cha rnams las srang re re lhan cig tu chu phul drug cu rtsa bzhi'i nang du bskol te khu ba brgyad cha gcig lus pa btsags la /
T16TD4434E:284a-11: 'o ma phul brgyad dang bskol te /
T16TD4434E:284a-12: 'o ma nyi tshe lus pa'i nang du /
T16TD4434E:284a-16: dug mo nyung gi shun lpags dang /
T16TD4434E:284a-17: ba ru ra rnams kyi phye ma zho gnyis gnyis dang /
T16TD4434E:284a-21: srog chags skams na gnas pa'i sha khu rnams ci ran pa dang /
T16TD4434E:284a-22: 'di rnams sbyar ba'i bkru sman drag po mas btang ba 'di ni rlung dang mkhris pa sel ba yin te /
T16TD4434E:284a-23: ro tsa bar byed cing me drod shin tu bskyed pa dang na ba dang /
T16TD4434E:284a-26: gcong chen po za byed kyi nad dang /
T16TD4434E:284a-28: phyi sa 'gags pa rnams kyang sel to //
T16TD4434E:284a-30: til mar cha bsnyams la de gnyis bsdoms pa'i tshad kyi kru trug tres bskol ba'i khu ba dang /
T16TD4434E:284a-31: shu ti'i phye ma srang gcig dang /
T16TD4434E:284a-32: rgyam tsha zho gnyis 'di rnams sbyar ba'i bkru sman drag po mas btang ba 'di ni cho ga bsrung mi dgos te ro tsa bar bya ba dang /
T16TD4434E:284a-34: sha skye bar bya ba dang /
T16TD4434E:284a-37: skran rnams bsal ba la dge ba yin te /
T16TD4434E:284a-38: gnod pa'i nyen du mi 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:284a-42: til mar rnams las srang gnyis gnyis dang /
T16TD4434E:284a-44: rgyam tsha zho gnyis gnyis te 'di rnams sbyar ba'i bkru sman drag po mas btang ba ni brtag par byed pa'i mchog yin te /
T16TD4434E:284a-45: de la mar gyi 'jam rtsi'i bcud mas btang ba'i tshad ni spyir srang gsum du bya'o //
T16TD4434E:284a-46: bkru sman drag po mas btang ba'i tshad ni de'i brgyad du bya'o //
T16TD4434E:284a-47: tshos par byed pa'i sman dang /
T16TD4434E:284b-0: bkru sman gnyis la ni sman gyi phye ma srang @284b re re btang ngo //
T16TD4434E:284b-1: yang nyams stobs kyis ji tsam nus pa dang sbyar ro //
T16TD4434E:284b-2: ji ltar shing gi rtsa ba chus bran na /
T16TD4434E:284b-3: lo ma sngo zhing snum pa skye ba de bzhin du mi la yang mar gyi 'jam rtsi'i bcud mas btang ba dang /
T16TD4434E:284b-4: bkru sman drag po mas btang ba'i cho ga 'di dag ltar btang na mdog snum zhing nyams stobs dang ldan par 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:284b-5: las rnam lnga'i le'u ste sum cu pa rdzogs so /
T16TD4434E:284b-7: // / da ni cho ga'i le'u bshad par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:284b-8: sgog skya la ni ro rnam pa drug las /
T16TD4434E:284b-9: skyur ba ma gtogs par mang ra ba dang /
T16TD4434E:284b-13: lan tshva'i ro 'di lnga yang yod de /
T16TD4434E:284b-14: de ni tshim pa med par byed pa yin no //
T16TD4434E:284b-15: de sman gzhan dang sbyar na nad gzhi gsum char yang sel to //
T16TD4434E:284b-16: de la mi mi na ba nyams stobs skye bar 'dod pas ni /
T16TD4434E:284b-17: dpyid zla 'bring po'i ngo la bza' bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:284b-18: nad yod pa la ni dus kun yang bza' bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:284b-19: sgog skya nar son cing rdo gu grung bor gyur la /
T16TD4434E:284b-20: skyon med cing yon tan dang ldan pa de nyid kyi khu ba cho ga bsrung bzhin du /
T16TD4434E:284b-21: gzar zhing zho gnyis gnyis kyis bskyed de btung bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:284b-22: de la srang gnyis sam bzhi 'am /
T16TD4434E:284b-23: drug gi bar du rab 'bring tha ma'i tshad las nyams stobs dang sbyar zhing btang bar bshad do //
T16TD4434E:284b-24: de la rlung dang bad kan gnyis la ni /
T16TD4434E:284b-25: sman pas rtsabs skyur po dang /
T16TD4434E:284b-26: tshva dang chang la sogs pas dbul /
T16TD4434E:284b-28: khu ba mngar po rnams kyis dbul lo //
T16TD4434E:284b-29: kha zas ni gro las byas pa'i bag / skam sa na gnas pa'i bya sha gang yin pa rnams kyi sha khu dang ldan par za zhing /
T16TD4434E:284b-32: mya ngan la sogs pa dang /
T16TD4434E:284b-34: kha zas mi 'ju ba rnams spang bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:284b-35: de'i cho ga ni nad las dpag cing /
T16TD4434E:284b-36: zhag bdun nam bdun gnyis sam /
T16TD4434E:284b-37: zhag bdun gsum gyi bar du tshad rab 'bring rnam pa gsum du shes par bya'o //
T16TD4434E:285a-0: de la sgog skya'i khu ba mar dang sbyar ba ni @285a * //
T16TD4434E:285a-2: til mar dang sbyar ba ni bad kan dang rlung sel to //
T16TD4434E:285a-3: tshil lam rkang dang sbyar ba ni glo brdol ba'am zad byed kyi nad las brta bar byed do //
T16TD4434E:285a-4: sgog skya zhib tu brdungs la 'o ma dang bskol te khar dang sbyar ba 'thung zhing /
T16TD4434E:285a-5: sman zhu ba'i 'og tu kha zas 'o ma 'am sha khu dang ldan par zos na /
T16TD4434E:285a-6: khrag lud pas nyam thag pa dang /
T16TD4434E:285a-11: brjed byed rnams sel zhing chag grugs byung ba dang /
T16TD4434E:285a-15: mo gsham rnams la bzang ngo //
T16TD4434E:285a-17: tshad pa be'u snabs su 'byung bas nyam thag pa dang /
T16TD4434E:285a-18: 'bras kyi phreng ba yod pa dang /
T16TD4434E:285a-19: lus shin tu rid pa dang /
T16TD4434E:285a-21: bud med bu nu bzhin pa rnams kyis ni btung bar mi bya'o //
T16TD4434E:285a-22: kun dong ni sgog skya las chung zad tsam gyis mthu chung ste de yang cho ga bzhin du bza' bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:285a-26: rtsa pa lnga pa bskol ba'i khu ba dang /
T16TD4434E:285a-27: srog chags skams na gnas pa'i sha khu rnams las gang yang rung ba dang sbyar te /
T16TD4434E:285a-28: bsros la nyams stobs dang sbyar zhing tshod ran par btung bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:285a-29: ae randa'i mar 'bras bu gsum bskol ba'i khu ba dang sbyar te btang na /
T16TD4434E:285a-30: bad kan dang mkhris pa sel to //
T16TD4434E:285a-31: rtsa ba bcu pa bskol ba'i khu ba dang sbyar te btang na rlung dang mkhris pa las gyur pa'i nad sel to //
T16TD4434E:285a-33: rgun chang gang yang rung ba dang sbyar te 'thungs na gcin sri ba dang rde'us 'gags pa sel to //
T16TD4434E:285a-34: 'o ma dang sbyar na rlung skran sel to //
T16TD4434E:285a-42: khrag lud pa nyi tshe ba rnams kyis ni btung bar mi bya'o //
T16TD4434E:285b-0: go byi'i cho ga ni go byi'i 'bras bu lnga cho ga bzhin du @285b ba'i gcin gyi nang du bskol te bzhi cha lus nas mnyes la tshig ma bor ba'i khu ba grang mo mchu dang rkan mar gyis bskus te btung zhing thabs de ltar nyin gcig bzhin du go byi'i 'bras bu lnga lngas bskyed /
T16TD4434E:285b-1: go byi'i 'bras bu bdun cu la thug gi bar du snga ma bzhin du btung /
T16TD4434E:285b-2: de nas nyin re bzhin lnga lngas phri ste /
T16TD4434E:285b-3: 'brum bu lnga la thug nas slar yang de bzhin du bskyed cing dbri'o //
T16TD4434E:285b-4: sman 'thungs pa zhu bar gyur pa'i 'og tu kha zas ni 'bras chan grang mo mar dang 'o ma bskol te bsgrangs pa dang ldan par bza' bya ste /
T16TD4434E:285b-5: sman bcud kyi len gyi cho ga 'dis ni yid gzhungs par byed cing /
T16TD4434E:285b-6: gnyer ma dang skra dkar med par byed la /
T16TD4434E:285b-9: khrag tshad dang srin bu'i nyes pa rnams sel to //
T16TD4434E:285b-10: khu chu la nad yod par gyur pa yang sbyong bar byed do //
T16TD4434E:285b-11: go byi'i mar nyams stobs dang sbyar zhing /
T16TD4434E:285b-12: zla ba gcig gi bar du ran par 'thungs na nad kyi gnod pa thams cad las thar te /
T16TD4434E:285b-13: lus brtan por lo brgya'i bar du 'tsho bar 'gyur ro //
T16TD4434E:285b-14: me dang nyi ma 'de ba dang /
T16TD4434E:285b-15: nyin par gnyid log pa dang /
T16TD4434E:285b-17: kha zas lci ba rnams ni spang bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:285b-18: sman gyi mjug bcad nas kyang ji srid kyi bar du sman btang ba'i dus kyi nyis 'gyur gyi bar du cho ga bsrung bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:285b-19: mkhris pa shas che ba'i mi la ni /
T16TD4434E:285b-20: sman 'di byed pa'i tshe khar 'brum pa 'byung ba dang /
T16TD4434E:285b-22: rims la sogs pas 'debs par 'gyur te /
T16TD4434E:285b-23: de la ni sman bsil ba'i lde gu'am khu ba grang mos lus byug pa dang /
T16TD4434E:285b-24: steng du blugs pa dang btung ba rnams bya'o //
T16TD4434E:285b-25: pi pi ling bskyed pa'i cho ga ni /
T16TD4434E:285b-26: 'o ma bskol te phyed du nas phyung ba'i nang du /
T16TD4434E:285b-27: pi pi ling 'brum bu lnga btags te btung zhing /
T16TD4434E:285b-28: de ltar zhag bcu'i bar du nyin re zhing pi pi ling 'brum bu lnga lngas bskyed de btung bar bya'o //
T16TD4434E:285b-29: de nas nyin re zhing pi pi ling lnga lngas phri ste //
T16TD4434E:285b-30: pi pi ling 'brum lnga la thug nas /
T16TD4434E:286a-0: yang snga ma bzhin du bskyed cing phri la @286a * //
T16TD4434E:286a-1: kha zas 'o ma dang ldan par bza' zhing cho gas bsrungs na /
T16TD4434E:286a-8: dmu rdzings rnams sel zhing rims ldang dub kyis dus mi 'dra ba med par byed do //
T16TD4434E:286a-10: brag zhun gser dang lcags la sogs pa las 'byung ste /
T16TD4434E:286a-11: de dag ni mthu dang ldan zhing /
T16TD4434E:286a-12: de dag gi mdog dang 'dra la /
T16TD4434E:286a-13: ba gcin gyi dri bro ba dang /
T16TD4434E:286a-14: snum zhing lci la rdo med pa bzang ste /
T16TD4434E:286a-15: nges chu chus bkrus ba dang /
T16TD4434E:286a-16: ba gcin gyi nang du mnye bas chog bzhin du btul nas /
T16TD4434E:286a-17: de'i phye mas nad gzhi gsum gang gi sman du btang ba de'i sman gyi sde tshan bskol ba'i khu bas lan mang du bsgo zhing bskams la /
T16TD4434E:286a-18: nad gzhi gang gi sman du btang ba de'i sman gyi sde tshan bskol ba'i khu ba dang sbyar te 'thungs na nad do cog sel to //
T16TD4434E:286a-19: cho ga de bzhin du drub mar chang gi phye ma yang sman bskol ba'i khu bas bsgo zhing sbyar te 'thungs na nad do cog sel to //
T16TD4434E:286a-20: sman 'di gnyis kyi cho ga byed pas thi ba'i sha dang /
T16TD4434E:286a-21: rgya sran bza' bar mi bya'o //
T16TD4434E:286a-22: aa ru ra'i cho ga ni /
T16TD4434E:286a-23: aa ru ra'i phye ma rgyam tsha dang sbyar na rlung sel to //
T16TD4434E:286a-24: mar dang sbyar na mkhris pa sel to //
T16TD4434E:286a-25: bca' sga dang sbyar na bad kan sel to //
T16TD4434E:286a-26: bu ram dang sbyar na nad do cog sel to //
T16TD4434E:286a-27: skyu ru ra'i cho ga ni /
T16TD4434E:286a-28: skyu ru ra'i khu ba phul gang la srang brgyad du brtsis pa'i phul bcu drug btsags la /
T16TD4434E:286a-29: bum pa sbrang rtsis bskus pa'i nang du blugs te kha bcad nas yun ring du bzhag la /
T16TD4434E:286a-31: dgun smad dam dbyar btung bar bya ste /
T16TD4434E:286a-33: 'o mar sbyar na khrag lud pa gyen du 'byung ba dang mkhris pa sel to //
T16TD4434E:286a-34: kha ra dang sbyar na skya rbab kyi nad sel cing /
T16TD4434E:286a-35: mo mtshan gyi khrag mi chod pa chod par byed do //
T16TD4434E:286a-36: sbrang rtsir sbyar na bad kan gyi nad sel to //
T16TD4434E:286a-37: tsha ba gsum dang sbyang na drod chung ba las drod skyed par byed do //
T16TD4434E:286a-38: sman so ma r'a dza dang sbyar na mdze nad sel to //
T16TD4434E:286b-0: dug @286b mo nyung gi shun lbags dang sbyar na gzhang 'brum sel to //
T16TD4434E:286b-1: 'di ltar bdag gis tshe'i rig byed kyi rgya mtsho drang srong gzhung la skyes kyi bu dang /
T16TD4434E:286b-2: drang srong rgyun shes kyi bu la sogs pa'i gzhung rnams bltas nas /
T16TD4434E:286b-3: gso ba'i dpyad kyi zer tsam gyi rgyud le'u sum cu rtsa gcig po 'di rnams rim bzhin phab cing sbyar ba ni /
T16TD4434E:286b-4: pho bo lha bsrungs skya rbab kyi nad kyis btab pas byed du bcug nas /
T16TD4434E:286b-5: de'i phyer sman dpyad 'di nyi mas bsrungs pas byas so //
T16TD4434E:286b-6: cho ga'i le'u ste sum cu rtsa gcig pa'o /
T16TD4434E:286b-8: // / sman dpyad gces pa grub pa zhes bya ba /
T16TD4434E:286b-9: nub phyogs pa rta mkhan bgrod dkas bsrungs ba'i bu nyi mas bsrungs pas byas pa rdzogs so //
T16TD4434E:286b-10: rgya gar gyi mkhan po dzi na mi tra dang /
T16TD4434E:286b-12: lo ts'a ba bande tsandras bsgyur te gtan la phab pa'o //
T16TD4434E:286b-13: bdag gis rig mchog gces grub 'di bris pas //
T16TD4434E:286b-14: rlung mkhris bad kan nad gzhi dug gsum dang //
T16TD4434E:286b-15: 'phral gyi rkyen gyur nyon mongs gsum brgyad kyis //
T16TD4434E:286b-16: mnar med sems can mtha' yas thams cad kun //
T16TD4434E:286b-17: sman rnams bdud rtsir gyur nas nyam thag pa'i //
T16TD4434E:286b-18: rlung mkhris dug gsum la sogs gtan spangs te //
T16TD4434E:286b-19: sa rab bgrod dka' lam gyi nyes bsal nas //
T16TD4434E:286b-20: g-yung drung bla med chen po myur thob shog //
